"), WE REPORTED NET EARNINGS OF $6.3 BILLION

AND DILUTED EARNINGS PER SHARE OF $4.71

COMPARED TO NET EARNINGS OF $5.4 BILLION

AND DILUTED EARNINGS PER SHARE OF $3.76

FOR THE FISCAL YEAR ENDED

FEBRUARY 2, 2014

("FISCAL

2013

"). THE RESULTS FOR FISCAL 2014 INCLUDED

$33 MILLION

OF PRETAX NET EXPENSES RELATED TO A BREACH OF OUR PAYMENT DATA SYSTEMS (THE "DATA BREACH"). THE RESULTS FOR FISCAL 2014 ALSO INCLUDED A

$323 MILLION

PRETAX GAIN RELATED TO THE SALE OF A PORTION OF OUR EQUITY OWNERSHIP IN HD SUPPLY HOLDINGS, INC. ("HD SUPPLY").

