. THIS CASH FLOW, ALONG WITH $2.0 BILLION OF LONG-TERM DEBT ISSUED IN FISCAL

2014

AND CASH ON HAND, WAS USED TO FUND

$7.0 BILLION

OF SHARE REPURCHASES, PAY

$2.5 BILLION

OF DIVIDENDS, FUND

$1.4 BILLION

IN CAPITAL EXPENDITURES, AND PAY FOR THE ACQUISITION OF HD SUPPLY HARDWARE SOLUTIONS.

OUR INVENTORY TURNOVER RATIO WAS

