. OUR RETURN ON INVESTED CAPITAL (COMPUTED ON NET OPERATING PROFIT AFTER TAX FOR THE TRAILING TWELVE MONTHS AND THE AVERAGE OF BEGINNING AND ENDING LONG-TERM DEBT AND EQUITY) WAS

24.9%

